opennlp.ccg.ngrams.kenlm
Class MurmurHash

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.ngrams.kenlm.MurmurHash

public final class MurmurHash
extends Object

MurmurHash 2.0. The murmur hash is a relative fast hash function from http://murmurhash.googlepages.com/ for platforms with efficient multiplication. This is a re-implementation of the original C code plus some additional features. Public domain.

Version:
1.0.2
Author:
Viliam Holub
